And the masked vigilante had more to contend with than his arch nemesis The Riddler. The stunt double, wearing a costume from the Dark Knight era, faced strong winds as he rode the attraction to 443ft. But he surveyed the city in safety, including the newly refurbished Big Ben minus the scaffolding that has been a fixture since 2017. In Warner Bros' latest dark film, Robert Pattinson, 35, plays the DC Comics hero. The Batman is out on Friday.